        "text_hash": "cd2b5c7e0b35f66ed82fb398a33b9f03543a4c215317ebbb720199b0e498dc91",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_a90e7efe16029c58abad2735",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "生命与生物术语表",
        "text_hash": "ce97e4fb718a8ae229b09ee0d4b614ab5c4166a8e858aab27d23939ea5a66cbf",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e5725a86f22013c6f8d7615d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "非生物的：环境中无生命的要素，如土壤、水和空气",
        "text_hash": "b0079db69eb6bf41cf98c16dc31403226fc96af5ab635367a2c259e413329d6f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_691b32668b12d043e9db38bf",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "适应 / 已适应：根据周围环境 / 环境来改变某物的外观或做某事的方式",
        "text_hash": "9fced0a0c0cd1e024e2408a9dbccd74b86865ccaadc4c8e4a175a00a82a19d6c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_4fbaf788d4f11244275ea500",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "两栖动物：脊椎动物中的一类，在其生命周期的不同时期生活在陆地和水中，是变温动物，皮肤裸露；其幼体在水中孵化并有鳃，后来转变为用肺呼吸的成体",
        "text_hash": "82eefc494e60b226a3f3f6c59f580917bb2f6c6e15e939b0fb77928affe6a799",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0b759f393e32b5809a4784c2",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "被子植物：有花并产生包裹在果实中的种子的植物",
        "text_hash": "1f487c55f93f81c9407a349ac71eb799810b44356d1c28b3b55aa05bf95b3903",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3873656aa7d762bc097c1242",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "触角（触角复数）：某些节肢动物（如昆虫和甲壳类动物）头部的两条细长部分之一，用于触觉、嗅觉和味觉",
        "text_hash": "e2e8a4ebeeb47da0d8aebd80d256d21f3a8e8de0943400480b97555b98111151",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e2edb0ae21748421fd1dac5d",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "花药：植物雄性生殖器官中含有花粉的部分",
        "text_hash": "8d4ed9ef8dd247274fcb7a08f5e70527456dc64f353f9b1a7959b03c199f6de2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_812a22f32c53fff9e9d16048",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "水生的：在水中或水附近的",
        "text_hash": "9fcf7d5e1da7348c71a889ee521772cdf815e7748c6d533610d90ec675f98b91",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c196603d9e4f191f30dadc4c",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "节肢动物：一大类具有坚硬身体、没有脊柱且腿分成若干节的动物中的任何一种",
        "text_hash": "06ff73dc6175aa6804d4d0e7d11845c917ee826c3e740545264ef0b3525c1f90",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ed85bbdd5d9e60077933f8f6",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "无性繁殖：植物和真菌的一种繁殖方式，不需要雄性和雌性生殖细胞融合来产生新的生物体",
        "text_hash": "aa0496e5e66dc061f8c10032c1b2c4e6a712532917f773a0a493a2bdbca58e5f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_260a3bdc1a9c2dcb431b046a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "大气：围绕地球的气体层",
        "text_hash": "1c9141dee6d31fb575db7cc3a7f71aa465b30687ffb4c9c47a54a937df43b0da",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_24cf25f81f9adf4df89cc6aa",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "生物圈：地球表面、水和大气中生命可以存在的部分（也是植物、动物和生物体可以生活的地方）",
        "text_hash": "8e5739065497a8a8502b2952bef5a586643e189d411d0589f310b8cf9e0596ba",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_fca1529604074b3830219b47",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "鳞茎：一种地下茎，带有一个或多个被叶或鳞片覆盖的芽，如洋葱和郁金香",
        "text_hash": "facec6b711e24e7759503313f84fa09155ca2a4a3fcdab9ff8dd657aeb91667a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_dd1b5d5c13c1d4f5a949fbaf",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "软骨：类似骨骼的坚韧、柔韧组织",
        "text_hash": "2d6455447974101325508d70e49d7fdcd7b47513ddd71b7f59e967fc05cf3197",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5ead4aa30976b08749ef4518",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "细胞：能够维持七项生命过程的生命最小结构单位或构成单元",
        "text_hash": "50161cf2337c2aac950da99810929321e2ed75f59bea13e7edeecc53f30c2650",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_7116b8e1cd3738997c2bc5eb",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "细胞呼吸：生物体中利用氧气从食物中释放能量，并释放二氧化碳作为副产物的过程",
        "text_hash": "ffefcc0ec22c645519378e4156cccab33e43e2c0a69f321978569eb96be41f83",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_bcd9f8b8380c5cc933dc2697",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "特征：使一事物区别于另一事物的典型特点或品质",
        "text_hash": "72fb67e671ba9420a55f07cc5746cef342c4fbe0888dec62268e891474f1e5fa",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_e7fa2d259bb75264f5dc81dd"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    }
  ],
